        "由题设可得 $\\overrightarrow{BA}\\cdot\\overrightarrow{AC}+\\overrightarrow{AC}\\cdot\\overrightarrow{BC}=0$，即 $\\overrightarrow{AC}\\cdot(\\overrightarrow{BA}+\\overrightarrow{BC})=0$。",
